Project Name: CO2 Australia Creating a Better Climate Project
Method: Carbon Credits (Carbon Farming Initiative) (Reforestation by Environmental or Mallee Plantings - FullCAM) Methodology Determination 2014
Project Description: This project establishes permanent plantings of Eucalyptus loxophleba and Eucalyptus polybractea trees on land that was previously used for agricultural purposes.
Project Area(s), where the project is an:
Details of the five parcels of land not supressed are: Lots 2, 10, 11, 23, 33, 41 and 43 of Deposited Plan 753082; Lot 85 of Deposited Plan 704703; Lot 1 of Deposited Plan 449213; Lots 7 and 51 of Deposited Plan 753138; Lots 7, 32 and 33 of Deposited Plan 752120; Lot 1 of Deposited Plan 1128884.                                                                                                                                                                                                                      



The project is located in the local government areas of Bland, Carrathool, Coolamon, Dubbo, Greater Hume Shire, Lachlan,  Narrandera, Narromine, Parkes and Wellington.



Partial Suppression of project details approved under section 169 of the Carbon Credits (Carbon Farming Initiative) Act 2011.
